race.comment: LIETUVA (2) has been out of the placings in two runs since a break, the latest when fifth, beaten 2.5 lengths, over 1400m at Eagle Farm after he was in contention on the turn. Should be peaking now and can find winning form this time. INSPIRED DREAM (7) travelled in a rearwards position then made some inroads and finished 4 lengths away in fourth last time out over 1200m at Gold Coast Poly a month ago. Steps up in journey today and is sure to be competitive. PROPHET OF BOOM (1) scored two back at Surat but was below her best last time when sixth over 1400m at Tara. Nicely placed to bounce back. GOOGAZ (4) next in line.
